title: Black Haze (2025)
description: Black Haze (2025) Manhwa A long time ago, the [Door] connecting us to another world opened. People began calling those who received the [Mark] along with special powers [Mages]. Ophion’s Tier 1 Mage, [Blow], is currently paying the price of fame after the events on ‘that day’. One day, he receives a very special contract. That is, to protect the second son of the Artian Ducal Family from being called an ‘Abomination’ in the [Helios Magic School]. And so, Blow ends up entering Helios while hiding his indentity under the name ‘Ruud Chrysi’… Can Blow truly complete his contract safely inside the hurricane of unexpected events? 블랙 헤이즈,
